something successful.

502
00:28:47,351 --> 00:28:49,562
Well, then you should
listen to Gordon.

503
00:28:49,603 --> 00:28:51,564
He's actually a genius.

504
00:28:51,605 --> 00:28:53,815
Why do you think
I chose him?

