523
00:29:48,995 --> 00:29:51,998
Yeah, well,
I got nothing but time.

524
00:29:58,756 --> 00:30:00,048
Clark, huh?

525
00:30:03,009 --> 00:30:06,846
Gordon is good.

526
00:30:06,888 --> 00:30:08,724
- Mm.
- He's really good.

527
00:30:08,766 --> 00:30:11,810
- Mm-hmm.
