00:31:32,766 --> 00:31:35,686
Listen, now, the--

554
00:31:35,728 --> 00:31:38,313
the theatrics
out there today.

555
00:31:38,355 --> 00:31:40,357
( sighs )

556
00:31:40,399 --> 00:31:42,234
Be more careful, Cam.

557
00:31:42,275 --> 00:31:46,905
I'm a big girl.
I can take care of myself.

558
00:31:46,946 --> 00:31:50,992
Oh, hell, I know that.
That's plain as day.
It's just...

559
00:31:51,034 --> 00:31:52,786
( sighs )

560
00:31:52,828 --> 00:31:54,287
Some of the people
around here,

561
00:31:54,329 --> 00:31:57,750
no matter what they say,
or even what they think--

562
00:31:57,791 --> 00:32:00,335
